<Defs>

    <TraitDef>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Student_Gehenna</defName>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>格黑娜学园学生</label>
				<description>{PAWN_nameDef}是格黑娜学园的学生。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<MoveSpeed>1.0</MoveSpeed>
					<HuntingStealth>0.5</HuntingStealth>
				</statOffsets>
				<skillGains>
					<Shooting>4</Shooting>
				</skillGains>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Hina</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>冷彻的会长</label>
				<description>日奈委员会虽然因为平日的压力总是想要偷懒，但是只要听到风纪有关的问题，就会变得很严肃且毫不犹豫，因此也被很多人所畏惧着。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<AimingDelayFactor>-0.5</AimingDelayFactor>
					<RangedCooldownFactor>-0.4</RangedCooldownFactor>
					<ShootingAccuracyPawn>0.55</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
                    <MeleeDodgeChance>0.05</MeleeDodgeChance>
                    <MentalBreakThreshold>-0.24</MentalBreakThreshold>
				</statOffsets>
                <statFactors>
                    <IncomingDamageFactor>0.3</IncomingDamageFactor>
                </statFactors>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

	<TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_HinaSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>慵懒的日奈</label>
				<description>尽管以冷冽的风纪委员会会长闻名，但是日奈其实也只是个普通的高中女生，对眼前看不到头的工作感到厌烦，想要休息和撒娇，也想要得到鼓励与安慰。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<PsychicSensitivity>0.15</PsychicSensitivity>
					<RestRateMultiplier>0.05</RestRateMultiplier>
					<GlobalLearningFactor>0.8</GlobalLearningFactor>
				</statOffsets>
                <disallowedMentalStates>
                    <li>InsultingSpree</li>
                    <li>TargetedInsultingSpree</li>
                </disallowedMentalStates>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Ako</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>亲切的行政官</label>
				<description>"亚子作为日奈的行政官平日里总是以亲切善良的样子待人，平时待人彬彬有礼。\n不过这只是公开时候这样，实际上私下日奈既高傲又神经质。"</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>0.2</SocialImpact>
					<GlobalLearningFactor>0.4</GlobalLearningFactor>
				</statOffsets>
                <disallowedMentalStates>
                    <li>InsultingSpree</li>
                    <li>TargetedInsultingSpree</li>
                </disallowedMentalStates>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
        <modExtensions>
			<li Class="AKE_OperatorExtension.DefExt_SkillLossRate">
				<skillLossFactor>0.85</skillLossFactor>
			</li>
		</modExtensions>
	</TraitDef>

	<TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_AkoSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>日奈的宠物</label>
				<description>虽然亚子在私下对他人非常高傲，但是她对日奈非常喜欢，也总是关心着日奈的一切。</description>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Iori</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>专家的威压</label>
				<description>伊织作为风纪委员的专家，总是冷静的处理格赫娜制造各种麻烦的问题学生，并且用压倒性强大实力处罚他们。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<MeleeDodgeChance>0.25</MeleeDodgeChance>
					<PainShockThreshold>-0.25</PainShockThreshold>
					<MoveSpeed>0.3</MoveSpeed>
                    <MentalBreakThreshold>-0.12</MentalBreakThreshold>
                    <ShootingAccuracyPawn>0.2</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
                    <SocialImpact>-0.05</SocialImpact>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

	<TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_IoriSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>倒霉蛋</label>
				<description>虽然伊织有着很强的实力，但是因为一遇到敌人就会冲上去，加上自己比较倒霉，所以总是吃瘪。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<IncomingDamageFactor>0.15</IncomingDamageFactor>
					<TradePriceImprovement>-0.35</TradePriceImprovement>
				</statOffsets>
                <statFactors>
                    <PawnTrapSpringChance>3</PawnTrapSpringChance>
                    <TameAnimalChance>0.2</TameAnimalChance>
                    <TrainAnimalChance>0.2</TrainAnimalChance>
                </statFactors>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Chinatsu</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>护理专家</label>
				<description>火宫千夏是负责风纪委全体的保健和后勤工作，平日的工作就是照顾因为工作劳累的其他部员，除此之外，也承担了大量其他风纪委不愿意负责的小事杂事，还有在必要时制止失控的亚子和伊织。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>0.1</SocialImpact>
					<MentalBreakThreshold>-0.15</MentalBreakThreshold>
                    <PsychicEntropyRecoveryRate MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Royalty">-0.5</PsychicEntropyRecoveryRate>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_Iroha</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>摸鱼达人</label>
				<description>伊吕波很讨厌真琴天天给万魔殿招来的各种麻烦，也很讨厌自己不得不在真琴的施压下忙这忙那给真琴和万魔殿擦屁股，因此平时的工作她从是能应付就应付过去。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<WorkSpeedGlobal>-0.25</WorkSpeedGlobal>
					<RestRateMultiplier>-0.15</RestRateMultiplier>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

	<TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>BA_Trait_IrohaSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>心思缜密</label>
				<description>与慵懒的行事成反比的是，伊吕波的心思其实相当缜密，比起真琴，她总是能发现很多细节问题，并且在社交上也相当克制。不过这不妨碍她总是直接的骂真琴蠢。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>0.24</SocialImpact>
					<GlobalLearningFactor>0.25</GlobalLearningFactor>
                    <ResearchSpeed>0.15</ResearchSpeed>
                    <MentalBreakThreshold>-0.09</MentalBreakThreshold>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
        <modExtensions>
			<li Class="AKE_OperatorExtension.DefExt_SkillLossRate">
				<skillLossFactor>0.8</skillLossFactor>
			</li>
		</modExtensions>
	</TraitDef>

